comments: I really liked this class. It\'s mostly all spent in the lab and you learn various techniques. Jay is very cool, the course is interesting and relatively easy.
The class is a 3-week whirlwind of experiments. You won\'t have time to breathe. The background reading could be better, but the course is great.
She taught me how to clone DNA. I don\'t know if I love her or hate her for it....
